title: Kiss Me
lyrics:
[intro]  (C)  (Cmaj7)  (C7)  (Cmaj7) x2
 
(C) Kiss me (Cmaj7) out of the bearded barley,
(C7) Nightly, (Cmaj7) beside the green, green grass
(C) Swing, swing, (Cmaj7) swing the spinning step
(C7) You'll wear those shoes and I will (F) wear that dress Oooh
 
[chorus]
(Dm) Kiss me (G)
(C) Beneath the (Am)milky twilight
(Dm) Lead me (G)
(C) Out on the (C7)moonlit floor
(Dm) Lift you (G)open hand
(C) Strike up the (Cmaj7)band, and make the (Am)fireflies dance,
(G)Silvermoon's spa-(F)arkling,
[single strum] (Gsus4)  (Gsus4)  (G-stop)
So kiss (C)me  (Cmaj7)  (C7)  (Cmaj7)
 
(C) Kiss me (Cmaj7) down by the broken tree house
(C7) Swing me, (Cmaj7) upon its hanging tire
(C) Bring, bring, (Cmaj7) bring your flowered hat
(C7) We'll take the trail marked on your (F) father's map Oooh
 
[chorus]
(Dm) Kiss me (G)
(C) Beneath the (Am)milky twilight
(Dm) Lead me (G)
(C) Out on the (C7)moonlit floor
(Dm) Lift you (G)open hand
(C) Strike up the (Cmaj7)band, and make the (Am)fireflies dance,
(G)Silvermoon's spa-(F)arkling,
[single strum] (Gsus4)  (Gsus4)  (G-stop)
So kiss (C)me  (Cmaj7)  (C7)  (Cmaj7)
 
[interlude - kazoo]   
(Dm)  (G)  (C)  (Am) 
(Dm)  (G)  (C)  (C7)
 
[chorus]
(Dm) Kiss me (G)
(C) Beneath the (Am)milky twilight
(Dm) Lead me (G)
(C) Out on the (C7)moonlit floor
(Dm) Lift you (G)open hand
(C) Strike up the (Cmaj7)band, and make the (Am)fireflies dance,
(G)Silvermoon's spa-(F)arkling,
[single strum] (Gsus4)  (Gsus4)  (G-stop)
So kiss (C)me  (Cmaj7)  (C7)  (Cmaj7) x4
So kiss (C-single strum)me [end]
